msgctxt "488_Player"
msgid "You're not doing so well... You'll just have to try harder."
msgstr "No se te está dando muy bien... Tienes que esforzarte más."

msgctxt "500_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Okay, I'll try..."
msgstr "Lo intentaré..."

msgctxt "524_Player"
msgid "Good work out there tonight. I think you're getting the hang of things."
msgstr "Buen trabajo el de esta noche. Creo que le estás agarrando el truco."

msgctxt "536_キャバ育名前"
msgid "I'm glad to hear you say that. I hope I can keep improving."
msgstr "I'm glad to hear you say that. I hope I can keep improving."

msgctxt "560_Player"
msgid "Great job out there tonight. I could tell you were giving it your all."
msgstr "Buen trabajo ahí fuera. Se nota que estábais dandolo todo."

msgctxt "572_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Thank you, I was really trying!"
msgstr "Thank you, I was really trying!"

msgctxt "608_Player"
msgid "Let's work on your presentation. Makeup, hair, posture...\\r\n"\n"All of these things send certain signals to a man."
msgstr "Vamos a trabajar en tu presentación. Maquillaje, peinado, postura...\\r\n"\n"Todas estas cosas envían ciertas señales a un hombre."

msgctxt "620_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Right. I'm all ears."
msgstr "Right. I'm all ears."

msgctxt "644_Player"
msgid "You're doing very well. Good job out there."
msgstr "Lo estás haciendo muy bien. Buen trabajo."

msgctxt "656_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Thank you. It's all thanks to your help!"
msgstr "Gracias. ¡Todo gracias a tu ayuda!"

msgctxt "680_Player"
msgid "Hmm... You still need a bit of work."
msgstr "Mmm... Aún tienes que mejorar."

msgctxt "692_キャバ育名前"
msgid "I'm sorry... I'll try harder next time."
msgstr "Lo siento... Me esforzaré más la próxima vez."

msgctxt "716_Player"
msgid "Okay, so today we're going to study a little trivia. No\\r\n"\n"matter what the conversation, it's always important to be\\r\n"\n"smart about what you say. \"Knowledge is power,\" right?"
msgstr "Bien, hoy vamos a estudiar un poco. No importa cuál\\r\n"\n"sea la conversación, siempre es importante ser inteligente\\r\n"\n"con lo que dices. \"El conocimiento es poder\", ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "728_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Of course. I look forward to learning from you."
msgstr "Of course. I look forward to learning from you."

msgctxt "752_Player"
msgid "You're doing very well. Good job out there."
msgstr "Lo estás haciendo muy bien. Buen trabajo."

msgctxt "764_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Well, that's because you're such a good teacher!"
msgstr "Bueno, ¡es porque eres un buen profesor!"

msgctxt "788_Player"
msgid "Hmm... You still need a bit of work."
msgstr "Mmm... Aún tienes que mejorar."

msgctxt "800_キャバ育名前"
msgid "I'm sorry... I'll try harder next time."
msgstr "Lo siento... Me esforzaré más la próxima vez."

msgctxt "824_Player"
msgid "Right now, I'd like to give you some conversation tips to\\r\n"\n"help you captivate the customers. Sound good?"
msgstr "Ahora me gustaría darte algunos consejos de conversación\\r\n"\n"para ayudarte a cautivar a los clientes. ¿Te parece bien?"

msgctxt "836_キャバ育名前"
msgid "That sounds great. I could use a few pointers."
msgstr "That sounds great. I could use a few pointers."

msgctxt "860_Player"
msgid "You're doing very well. Good job out there."
msgstr "Lo estás haciendo muy bien. Buen trabajo."

msgctxt "872_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Thank you. It's all due to your help."
msgstr "Thank you. It's all due to your help."

msgctxt "896_Player"
msgid "Hmm... You still need a bit of work."
msgstr "Mmm... Aún tienes que mejorar."

msgctxt "908_キャバ育名前"
msgid "I'm sorry... I'll try harder next time."
msgstr "Lo siento... Me esforzaré más la próxima vez."

msgctxt "932_Player"
msgid "I think you should spend your downtime doing whatever you like. Relax."
msgstr "Creo que deberías pasar tu tiempo libre haciendo lo que quieras. Relajate."

msgctxt "944_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Really? Thank you!"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "968_Player"
msgid "Did you make the most of your time? You seem pretty relaxed now."
msgstr "¿Te la pasaste bien? Te ves bastante bien."

msgctxt "980_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Yes! I feel a lot better."
msgstr "¡Sí! Me siento mucho mejor."

msgctxt "1004_Player"
msgid "Well? Had a good break?"
msgstr "Well? Had a good break?"

msgctxt "1016_キャバ育名前"
msgid "No. Somehow, I just couldn't relax."
msgstr "No. Somehow, I just couldn't relax."

msgctxt "1040_Player"
msgid "Today, we're going to work on your weak points. Now I know I\\r\n"\n"might come off a little blunt, but bear with it, okay?"
msgstr "Vamos a mejorar tus puntos débiles. Sé que puedo\n"\n"llegar a ser un poco brusco, pero tenme paciencia, ¿sí?"

msgctxt "1052_キャバ育名前"
msgid "All right..."
msgstr "Claro..."

msgctxt "1076_Player"
msgid "All right, now think about what I told you and give it your full effort next time."
msgstr "Muy bien, ahora piensa en lo que te he dicho y esfuérzate al máximo la próxima vez."

msgctxt "1088_キャバ育名前"
msgid "I will. Thank you!"
msgstr "Lo haré. ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "1112_Player"
msgid "(I don't think any of that really got through to her...)"
msgstr "(No creo que haya llegado a entenderlo...)"

msgctxt "1124_キャバ育名前"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1148_Player"
msgid "I think you should take some time off for yourself and relax for a bit."
msgstr "Creo que deberías tomarte un tiempo y relajarte un poco."

msgctxt "1160_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Okay! Thank you!"
msgstr "Okay! Thank you!"

msgctxt "1184_Player"
msgid "How was it? Did you get some relaxing in?"
msgstr "¿Y bien? ¿Te sientes mucho mejor ahora?"

msgctxt "1196_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Oh, yes! Thank you!"
msgstr "Oh sí. ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "1220_Player"
msgid "Did you have a good break?"
msgstr "¿Descansaste bien?"

msgctxt "1232_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Not really..."
msgstr "En realidad no..."

msgctxt "1256_Player"
msgid "Today, we're going to find a way to keep you motivated and positive. Sound good?"
msgstr "Hoy vamos a encontrar la manera en que te sientas motivada y positiva. ¿Qué te parece?"

msgctxt "1268_キャバ育名前"
msgid "All right. I can get behind that!"
msgstr "Sí. ¡Puedo hacerlo!"

msgctxt "1292_Player"
msgid "What do you think? Are you feeling any more positive?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal? ¿Te sientes mucho mejor?"

msgctxt "1304_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Oh, yes! Thank you!"
msgstr "Oh sí. ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "1328_Player"
msgid "How was that? Are you seeing the positive side of things a little more?"
msgstr "¿Y qué tal? ¿Ya le estás viendo el lado positivo a las cosas?"

msgctxt "1340_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Not really..."
msgstr "En realidad no..."

